  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unserious Sandbox is a single-player casual game with some unserious parkour.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391340/extras/b49571e52b2862b8091638f0318c9f8d.avif?t=1762218653\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391340/extras_big/b49571e52b2862b8091638f0318c9f8d.avif?t=1762218653 width=800 height=258 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Traversal</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traversal is a skill-based movement game, like KZ, Surf, or Minecraft parkour. The core of traversal is about using as little movement input as possible.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391340/extras/38422293a866945e5e1b681efdcf793e.poster.avif?t=1762218653\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391340/extras/38422293a866945e5e1b681efdcf793e.webm?t=1762218653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391340/extras/38422293a866945e5e1b681efdcf793e.mp4?t=1762218653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ragdoll Physics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with ragdoll physics in sandbox maps. Embrace the chaos and master the art of falling flat...?<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391340/extras/6c77ace4c06315c8714f769febae326c.poster.avif?t=1762218653\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391340/extras/6c77ace4c06315c8714f769febae326c.webm?t=1762218653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391340/extras/6c77ace4c06315c8714f769febae326c.mp4?t=1762218653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Sandbox</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, a Sandbox learned two words: <strong><i>Unseriverse, Susbicious.</i></strong> Then, the Sandbox became unserious and began parkour.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391340/extras/42e1ec152072ecb4ef22e28ba816572d.avif?t=1762218653\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391340/extras_big/42e1ec152072ecb4ef22e28ba816572d.avif?t=1762218653 width=800 height=534 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unserious Sandbox is a single-player casual game with some unserious parkour.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391340/extras/b49571e52b2862b8091638f0318c9f8d.avif?t=1762218653\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391340/extras_big/b49571e52b2862b8091638f0318c9f8d.avif?t=1762218653 width=800 height=258 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Traversal</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traversal is a skill-based movement game, like KZ, Surf, or Minecraft parkour. The core of traversal is about using as little movement input as possible.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391340/extras/38422293a866945e5e1b681efdcf793e.poster.avif?t=1762218653\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391340/extras/38422293a866945e5e1b681efdcf793e.webm?t=1762218653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391340/extras/38422293a866945e5e1b681efdcf793e.mp4?t=1762218653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ragdoll Physics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with ragdoll physics in sandbox maps. Embrace the chaos and master the art of falling flat...?<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391340/extras/6c77ace4c06315c8714f769febae326c.poster.avif?t=1762218653\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391340/extras/6c77ace4c06315c8714f769febae326c.webm?t=1762218653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391340/extras/6c77ace4c06315c8714f769febae326c.mp4?t=1762218653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Sandbox</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, a Sandbox learned two words: <strong><i>Unseriverse, Susbicious.</i></strong> Then, the Sandbox became unserious and began parkour.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391340/extras/42e1ec152072ecb4ef22e28ba816572d.avif?t=1762218653\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391340/extras_big/42e1ec152072ecb4ef22e28ba816572d.avif?t=1762218653 width=800 height=534 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
